#ROOM
Vnum     27500
Name     &OThe Stonetalon Pass&d~
Sector   mountain~
Desc     You stand at the entrance to the Stonetalon Mountains. The wide, dusty
plains of the Barrens drop away behind you as the path begins a steep,
winding ascent into the jagged grey peaks.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    26512
Desc      Back to the Barrens.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    27501
Desc      Higher into the mountains.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 27500 2 27500
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     27501
Name     &OThe Greatwood Vale - Entrance&d~
Sector   forest~
Desc     Surprisingly, the lower elevations of the mountains are lush and green.
Ancient trees cling to the rocky slopes, and a cool breeze carries the
scent of pine. The path splits here, heading north and west.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    27500
Desc      The mountain pass.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    27502
Desc      Toward Windshear Crag.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    27510
Desc      Toward the Charred Vale.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 27507 1 27501
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     27502
Name     &rWindshear Crag - Lower Shelf&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     The natural beauty of the vale is suddenly replaced by the sounds of
industry. Large wooden scaffolds and steam-powered drills have been
erected along the cliffs. The Venture Company has arrived.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    27501
Desc      Back to the vale.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    27503
Desc      Toward the logging camp.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 27501 3 27502
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     27503
Name     &rThe Venture Co. Logging Camp&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     A bustling hive of goblin activity. Goblins scurry about with clipboards,
while massive saws chew through the ancient timber of the mountains.
The air is thick with black smoke and the smell of hot grease.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    27502
Desc      The lower shelf.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    27504
Desc      The Windshear Mine.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    27505
Desc      Braun's Tool Shed.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 27510 1 27503
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     27504
Name     &dThe Windshear Mine&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors dark~
Desc     The entrance to a deep, dark tunnel carved into the side of the
mountain. The sound of pickaxes hitting stone echoes from within,
along with the occasional high-pitched squeak of a kobold.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    27503
Desc      The logging camp.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 27514 4 27504
Reset O 0 27512 1 27504
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     27505
Name     &xBraun's Tool Shed&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A small, sturdy shack filled with various mechanical parts, rusted
wrenches, and bundles of dynamite. Braun Wheelyam uses this space to
repair equipment—for a steep price.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    27503
Desc      The logging camp.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 27506 1 27505
Reset O 0 27504 1 27505
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     27506
Name     &OThe High Road&d~
Sector   mountain~
Desc     The road climbs higher, hugging the side of a massive precipice. Below,
the Windshear Crag looks like a scar on the land. To the north, the
peaks are perpetually shrouded in mist.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    27503
Desc      The logging camp.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    27507
Desc      Toward Sun Rock Retreat.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     27507
Name     &OEntrance to Sun Rock&d~
Sector   mountain~
Desc     The path narrows into a defensible canyon. Massive totems made of
cedar and stone stand on either side of the trail, marking the
territory of the Horde.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    27506
Desc      The high road.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    27508
Desc      Sun Rock Retreat.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 27503 2 27507
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     27508
Name     &gSun Rock Retreat - The Circle&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     A peaceful sanctuary nestled in a high-altitude basin. Tauren tents
surround a central fire pit where elders gather to speak with the
spirits. A crystal-clear pond sits at the northern end.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    27507
Desc      The entrance.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    27509
Desc      The Shaman's Overlook.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 27508 1 27508
Reset O 0 27501 1 27508
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     27509
Name     &gThe Shaman's Overlook&d~
Sector   mountain~
Desc     From this vantage point, you can see the entirety of the Stonetalon
range. The air is thin and cold. To the northwest, the mountains
become even more rugged and inhospitable.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    27508
Desc      The retreat.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    27520
Desc      The path to the Peak.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     27510
Name     &dThe Road to the Charred Vale&d~
Sector   mountain~
Desc     As you head west, the vegetation begins to die. The trees are
stunted and black, and the ground is covered in a fine layer of
grey ash. The air grows uncomfortably warm.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    27501
Desc      The Greatwood Vale.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    27511
Desc      The Scorched Basin.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     27511
Name     &dThe Scorched Basin&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     This entire valley was decimated by a magical fire of immense power.
Twisted, blackened trunks of ancient trees stand like skeletons against
the orange sky. Small fires still flicker in the cracks of the earth.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    27510
Desc      The road back.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    27512
Desc      The heart of the vale.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 27505 3 27511
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     27512
Name     &dThe Charred Vale - Heart&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     The devastation here is absolute. The ground is molten in some places,
and the air is thick with the scent of sulfur and old smoke. Dark
spirits of fire roam the ruins of the forest.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    27511
Desc      The basin.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    27513
Desc      Toward Mirkfallon Post.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset O 0 27505 2 27512
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     27513
Name     &gMirkfallon Post - Approach&d~
Sector   mountain~
Desc     The ash begins to clear as the path climbs north away from the
Charred Vale. A small Night Elf outpost is visible ahead, guarded by
Sentinels determined to protect the remaining green lands.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    27512
Desc      The Charred Vale.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    27514
Desc      Mirkfallon Post.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 27504 2 27513
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     27514
Name     &gMirkfallon Post&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     A modest Alliance encampment built on a high ridge. The Sentinels
here keep a close eye on both the Venture Company to the east and the
corruption of the Charred Vale to the south.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    27513
Desc      The approach.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    27515
Desc      The Talon Den.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset O 0 27507 1 27514
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     27515
Name     &gThe Talon Den - Entrance&d~
Sector   forest~
Desc     A lush, hidden valley protected by the mountains. This is one of the
few places in Stonetalon where the wildlife still thrives. The entrance
to an underground barrow den is hidden behind a waterfall.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    27514
Desc      Mirkfallon Post.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    28011
Desc      Into Ashenvale (Mystral Lake).
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 27513 2 27515
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     27516
Name     &OThe Webbed Pass&d~
Sector   mountain~
Desc     The mountain path is choked with thick, sticky spider webs. Large
cocoons hang from the rock walls, twitching occasionally. The air is
silent, save for the sound of skittering legs.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    27517
Desc      Deep into the pass.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    27506
Desc      The high road.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 27502 3 27516
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     27517
Name     &OThe Searing Chasm&d~
Sector   mountain~
Desc     A deep crack in the mountain floor reveals a flow of lava far below.
The heat is intense, and the path narrows to a precarious ledge.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    27516
Desc      The webbed pass.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    27518
Desc      Grimtotem Post.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     27518
Name     &dThe Grimtotem Post&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     A dark and unwelcoming camp. Unlike the Tauren of Sun Rock, these
warriors are aggressive and suspicious. Their tents are made of dark
leather and decorated with the bones of their enemies.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    27517
Desc      The chasm.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 27512 3 27518
Reset O 0 27511 1 27518
#ENDROOM

