Name     &gPath to Stonetalon Peak&d~
Sector   mountain~
Desc     The path becomes a series of switchbacks as it nears the highest
point in the range. The air is thin, and patches of snow cling to the
shadowed crevices.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    27509
Desc      The overlook.
~
#ENDEXIT
