#ROOM
Vnum     27521
Name     &gStonetalon Peak&d~
Sector   mountain~
Desc     You have reached the highest summit. The view is staggering, stretching
from the Great Sea to the west to the Barrens in the east. An ancient,
ethereal energy permeates the air here.
~
#EXIT
Direction down~
ToRoom    27520
Desc      The path down.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 27511 1 27521
Reset O 0 27514 1 27521
