#ROOM
Vnum     27522
Name     &OThe Bloodfury Hills&d~
Sector   hills~
Desc     The northern slopes of the mountains are home to the Bloodfury
harpy tribe. Their nests are built into the high cliffs, and their
screeches echo through the canyons.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    27508
Desc      Sun Rock Retreat.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    27523
Desc      The Harpy Rookery.
~
#ENDEXIT
