#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     27523
Name     &OThe Bloodfury Rookery&d~
Sector   hills~
Desc     The stench of filth and rotting meat is overwhelming. The ground is
carpeted with feathers and bones. Harpies dive from the sky to protect
